# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Production Secrets Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# This file contains templates for SECRETS that must be set in Cloudflare Workers.
# These values are NEVER committed to the repository - they must be set using
# Cloudflare's secrets management.
#
# Setting secrets in Cloudflare:
#   wrangler secret put SECRET_NAME
#   (You will be prompted to enter the value)
#
# PUBLIC environment variables are configured in wrangler.jsonc under "vars".
# See wrangler.jsonc for the complete list of public configuration.
#
# For GitHub Actions deployment, these secrets must also be set as GitHub repository secrets.
# See docs/GETTING_STARTED.md for step-by-step setup instructions.
#
# Quick Reference:
#   • Public vars location:    wrangler.jsonc (vars section)
#   • Complete reference:      docs/ENVIRONMENT_VARIABLES.md
#   • Setup guide:             docs/GETTING_STARTED.md
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required Secrets
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Database Authentication
# Pairs with: TURSO_DATABASE_URL in wrangler.jsonc
# Get from: Turso dashboard > Database > Settings > Auth Token
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_turso_auth_token

# NextAuth.js Encryption Secret
# CRITICAL: Generate a new secret for production using either:
#   • npx auth secret --raw
#   • openssl rand -base64 32
# Must be at least 32 characters for security
AUTH_SECRET=generate_a_new_secret_for_production

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional Secrets (uncomment and set when using these features)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google OAuth Authentication
# Required if: Using Google sign-in (AUTH_GOOGLE_ID is set in wrangler.jsonc)
# Pairs with: AUTH_GOOGLE_ID in wrangler.jsonc
# Get from: Google Cloud Console > Credentials > OAuth 2.0 Client > Client Secret
# Format: GOCSPX-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET=GOCSPX-your_google_oauth_client_secret

# Email Service (Mailgun)
# Required if: Sending transactional emails (magic links, notifications)
# Get from: Mailgun dashboard > Settings > API Keys
# AUTH_MAILGUN_KEY=your_mailgun_api_key

# AI Features (OpenAI)
# Required if: Using AI-powered meal generation, recipe suggestions
# Get from: OpenAI dashboard > API Keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your_openai_api_key_here
